snippet.title: Mannat Har khushi paane ki | Episode 1 | 06 January 25 | Mannat's special day
snippet.description:
ðŸ“² Download JioCinema: https://bit.ly/3Be09Z3

Mannat Har khushi paane ki | Episode 1 | 06 January 25

Sonia abandons her newborn, but Shruti rescues the baby girl from the seashore and names her Mannat. Twenty-three years later, Mannat dreams of becoming the world's best chef. Will her journey lead her to uncover the truth about her past?

-------------------

Abandoned as a newborn by her own heartless mother and raised by her resilient maasi, Shruti, Mannat grows up to be a passionate and ambitious chef, unaware of her mysterious origins. Her journey intertwines with that of Vikrant, a successful buisnessman (restaurateur), as they bond over their love for cooking amidst the vibrant backdrop of Mumbai's chawls and elite culinary spaces. Mannatâ€™s biological mother is none other than Aishwarya, a wealthy and manipulative woman determined to keep her secrets buried who is also Mannat's boss at Mezbaani where she works as a junior chef. Life takes a dramatic turn when Mannat discovers Shruti is not her biological mother, propelling her on a desperate quest to save Shrutiâ€™s life by finding her real mother for a liver transplant. Amidst these revelations, Mannat finds her strongest support in Vikrant, the prince charming of her life, who stands by her side, offering unwavering encouragement as she navigates the challenges life throws her way. As Mannatâ€™s rising career, Shrutiâ€™s failing health, and the revelations of a hidden past collide, Mannat faces a whirlwind of love, betrayal, and self-discovery. Will her dreams and resilience help her overcome the storm, or will the weight of her past keep her from achieving her destiny?


Main Cast and Their Characters:
Ayesha Singh as Mannat
Adnan Khan(Vikrant
Mona Vasu as Aishwarya
Sharain Khanduja as Mallika
Mamta Verma as Shruti
Delnaaz Irani as Harneet
Hasan Zaidi as Gagan
Karan Godhwami as Puneet
Swati Anand as Neetu
Rushad Rana as Rony

snippet.title: Sankranthiki Vasthunam Trailer - Victory Venkatesh | Anil Ravipudi | Dil Raju | Bheems Ceciroleo
snippet.description:
Watch #SankranthikiVasthunamTrailer here!!

#SankranthikiVasthunam is the Hattrick film under the collaboration of Victory #venkateshdaggubati, Hit Machine Director #AnilRavipudi and Blockbuster Producers Dilraju and Shirish. Touted as an extraordinary triangular crime entertainer, revolving around three characters- the protagonist, his ex-girlfriend, and his excellent wife. Produced by Sri Venkateswara Creations on a massive scale.

Meenakshi Chaudhary and Aishwarya Rajesh are the heroines opposite Venkatesh. Music is composed by Bheems Ceciroleo, Cinematography by Sameer Reddy, Production Designing by A S Prakash. 

Grand Release WorldWide On Jan 14, 2025. 

Cast:Venkatesh Daggubati, Meenakshi Chaudhary, Aishwarya Rajesh, Upendra Limaye, Sai Kumar, Naresh, VT Ganesh, Prithviraj, Srinivas Avasarala, Muralidhar Goud, Pammi Sai, Sai Srinivas, Anand Raj, Mahesh Balaraj, Pradeep Kabra, and Chitti etc.,

Get ready to laugh out loud with Zakir Khan in this stand-up comedy video where he dives into the rollercoaster ride of relationships! Zakir takes on the role of a funny relationship coach, sharing his hilarious tips and relatable stories about love's ups and downs. With his unique style of mixing humor with real-life advice, he makes understanding relationships a fun experience. So, sit back, relax, and enjoy as Zakir Khan shows us how to navigate the crazy world of love while keeping it lighthearted and entertaining!

snippet.description:
Madha Gaja Raja is an upcoming Indian Tamil-language action comedy film directed by Sundar C and produced by Gemini Film Circuit. It stars Vishal, Anjali and Varalaxmi Sarathkumar in the leading roles, while Santhanam and Sonu Sood play other pivotal supporting roles. The film began production in 2012 and was completed by 2013, but remained unreleased for over a decade due to financial troubles. It is scheduled to release in theatres on 12 January 2025, during the Pongal weekend. Madha Gaja Raja pre release event happened in chennai today. Lajja Shankar is attacked by all of them together, yet he manages to escape from their grasp and runs away | Sangharsh Movie Scenes

With children disappearing, mysteriously, CBI trainee, Reet Oberoi, is assigned to the case. Reet discovers that the missing children are being offered as sacrifices by Lajja Shankar Pandey (Ashutosh Rana), a religious fanatic. Unable to deal with Pandey herself, Reet gets Aman Varma to help her. However things aren't all that smooth for Aman. Will Reet and Aman subdue the evil fanatic, Pandey?

#GopalBhar #sonyaath #à¦—à§‹à¦ªà¦¾à¦²à¦­à¦° 

About Gopal Bhar:
-----------------------------
Gopal Bhar was a legendary court jester in medieval Bengal. He was in the court of Raja Krishnachandra, the famous king of Nadia in the 18th century AD. Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him as a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers.

Mangal Lakshmi unfolds as a poignant narrative, delving into the profound connection shared between two sisters, Mangal and Lakshmi. Set against life's myriad experiences, the story chronicles Mangal's odyssey in search of the ideal match, a 'dulha', for her cherished sibling, Lakshmi. As the tale progresses, it gracefully illustrates the intricacies of love, the resilience required to overcome trials, and the unwavering resolve that propels Mangal forward on her quest.
